author: Mike Colias
title: Cadillac and Lincoln Look to Give Their SUVs More Sex Appeal
text:
It’s been decades since the two U.S. luxury car divisions—Cadillac and Lincoln—put the luxury sport-utility vehicle on the map, equipping roomy off-roaders like the iconic Cadillac Escalade with thirsty engines and plenty of bling.
Now, the U.S. brands are playing a high stakes game of catch-up.
